@node about_fn.man "About FidoNet.MAN"

                         TrapDoor's FidoNet Manual
                        Thursday 05-Nov-92 10:24:11
                          Copyright (c) 1989-1992
                   Maximilian Hantsch and Martin Laubach
                            All rights reserved






